---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="Development | YApi Plugin" description="Development notes for the YApi Cursor plugin and its Pages site.">
  <article class="doc-article">
    <p class="eyebrow">Development</p>
    <h1>Local development</h1>
    <p>
      The repository now includes both the Cursor plugin files and a lightweight Astro site for GitHub Pages.
    </p>

    <h2>Useful commands</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>npm test</code></li>
      <li><code>npm run validate</code></li>
      <li><code>npm run dev</code></li>
      <li><code>npm run build</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Structure</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>skills/</code> and <code>commands/</code> power the Cursor plugin</li>
      <li><code>scripts/</code> wrap the local <code>yapi</code> CLI</li>
      <li><code>src/pages/</code> and <code>src/layouts/</code> power GitHub Pages</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
